title: Available 1 Bed 1 Bath
posting_body: ['Austin, 78751', 'E 45th Street', '$1150', '1 Bedroom', '***Availability and pricing is real-time and can change daily and vary by lease term***', 'These apartments feature a living room, dining room, and a kitchen with standard appliances, standard countertops, a dishwasher, and disposal.', 'The bedroom(s) have a closet and the bathroom(s) include a soaking tub.', 'Features central A/C, central heat, and ceiling fans.', 'Select units have microwaves, separate dining rooms, bay windows and a fireplace.', 'Community amenities include a swimming pool, grilling area, emergency maintenance, on site management and on site laundry.', 'UTILITIES.', 'Pets are welcome.', 'Off-street unassigned lot parking.', 'Less than a ten-minute commute to I-35.', '***PHOTOS ARE AN EXAMPLE OF SIMILAR UNITS WITHIN THE BUILDING, ACTUAL UNIT', 'MAY VARY***', 'Contact Agent:', 'Dave Burroughs', 'Independent Agents Austin TX', 'show contact info', 'Follow us on Twitter @RentalBeast', 'Find us on Facebook: <URL>']
